Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:42.69,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}摔了一跤 擦破了皮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:49.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}滲出了血 隱隱作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:54.82,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}別擔心啦 很快就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:24:00.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}明天就會結上層痂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:06.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}從海角邊 開出葉舟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:12.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}張開風帆 隨風而行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:19.14,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}我自現在 離開土地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:25.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}向著七海之遼前進
